Provides the kernel for a Xen instance on Amazons EC2.

@author Gunnar Wrobel <p@rdus.de>
@version 1.0
@package tool_ec2_kernel

@module os_gentoo      The os_gentoo module is required for Gentoo specific
                       package installation.

@fact operatingsystem  Allows to choose the correct package name
                       depending on the operating system. In addition
                       required to set additional tasks depending on
                       the distribution.

@param hardwaremodel   Used to determine the kernel modules that should
                       be downloaded.
@param architecture    Used to determine the kernel configuration.
